t the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, buy it to wear on Fridays and days he receives delegations. The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, this cloak is worn by one who has no share in the Hereafter.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33411,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/10\/aisha-sudden-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":17282,"position":1},"title":"Aisha on Death: Sudden death is mercy for believers, regret for wicked","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Ahwas reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cA sudden death is mercy for the believer and regretful for the wicked.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 12007 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0635\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u0627 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064f\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064c \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0641\u064c\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/near-far-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":17282,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Charity to near neighbors before far neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I have two neighbors; to whom should I send my gifts?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTo the neighbor who is closest to your door.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/generosity-mothers-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":17282,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Generosity: None more generous than Aisha and Asma","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Zubayr reported: I have not seen anyone more generous than Aisha and Asma', though their generosity was different. Aisha would gather things and after they had been collected, she would share them. As for Asma', should would not leave anything for tomorrow. Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 280 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/give-gifts-love-one-another\/","url_meta":{"origin":17282,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Gifts: Give each other gifts, you will love each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGive each other gifts and you will love each other.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 594 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to\u00a0Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u200f \u062a\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0627 594 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a 3\/1047 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062d\u062f\u062b \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u062c\u0631\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/07\/prophet-fun-wives-play-race\/","url_meta":{"origin":17282,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: The Prophet has fun with his wives","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She was with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while on a journey. Aisha said, \u201cI raced him on foot and I outran him, but when I gained some weight, I raced him again and he outran me. The Prophet said